body:
Test case
```java
@Test
    public void freesPingFrames() {
        ByteBuf content = UnpooledByteBufAllocator.DEFAULT.buffer(8).writeLong(0);
        DefaultHttp2PingFrame frame = new DefaultHttp2PingFrame(content);
        assertEquals(1, content.refCnt());
        codec.onHttp2Frame(frame);
        assertEquals(0, content.refCnt());
    }
```
 posted [here](https://github.com/bryce-anderson/netty/commit/37cdcd4defa853e5b9883c9bbea60e91a72ac5c6#diff-da759abb652d5db65698f9baf72b9ed2) results in
```
java.lang.AssertionError: 
Expected :0
Actual   :1

io.netty.handler.codec.http2.Http2MultiplexCodecTest.freesPingFrames(Http2MultiplexCodecTest.java:134)
```
